YELLOW FEVER - BRAZIL
*********************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Yellow fever - Brazil & French Guiana 980529074829
Yellow fever - Brazil (Amazonia) 980709204514
